something to meditate on while l consider a new career.

01:20:47.600 --> 01:20:50.839
Mortimer Granville, you're a good doctor, and you should remain one

01:20:51.160 --> 01:20:54.200
lnstead of leaching and bleeding
people in cutting them up to no purpose

01:20:54.200 --> 01:20:57.519
you, have invented a machine that does harm to no one

01:20:57.680 --> 01:21:00.399
and makes anyone had comes into contact with to feel better.

01:21:01.960 --> 01:21:05.679
l should think there a very few doctors in history
that could have a glimpse of such accomplishment.

01:21:08.680 --> 01:21:10.239
You are a confounding woman.

01:21:10.400 --> 01:21:13.839
You're all fier and brimstone in one minute,
compliments and common sense the next.

01:21:14.000 --> 01:21:15.772
I am a woman like any other.

01:21:16.120 --> 01:21:18.408
No, no. You're quite unlike any women l've ever met.

01:21:19.440 --> 01:21:20.423
Will you be alright?

01:21:20.760 --> 01:21:23.165
l'm fine. l've got lots of friends in prison.

01:21:32.388 --> 01:21:33.388
Mortimer

01:21:35.120 --> 01:21:36.639
Thought l might find you here.

01:21:44.360 --> 01:21:46.439
l've been thinking a lot about my future.

01:21:47.160 --> 01:21:49.120
And...well, actually

01:21:49.120 --> 01:21:51.279
l was wondering if you might give me a reading.

01:21:52.240 --> 01:21:54.279
l'm sorry. l've giving up phrenology.

01:21:54.280 --> 01:21:56.879
Oh, Emily, l'm...

01:21:57.400 --> 01:21:58.479
l'm so sorry.

01:21:58.720 --> 01:21:59.759
Don't be.

01:22:01.560 --> 01:22:04.520
Charlotte's trial was a revelation for me as well.

01:22:04.520 --> 01:22:07.938
l realized... l haven't been living my life at all.

01:22:08.320 --> 01:22:10.720
l've been living my father's idea what my life should be

01:22:10.720 --> 01:22:12.639
Phrenology, Chopin.

01:22:14.960 --> 01:22:16.439
Even you, Mortimer.

01:22:18.400 --> 01:22:19.479
You seem happy.

01:22:19.880 --> 01:22:20.879
l am.

01:22:21.520 --> 01:22:25.640
After all, life will always
be to large extent to what we ourselves make it.

01:22:25.640 --> 01:22:29.679
The inimitable Mr. Smiles.
